```{r pancreas 32413172, include=FALSE}

PMID_32413172 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32413172', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32413172 <- paste0(PMID_32413172$journal,' ', PMID_32413172$year, ' ', PMID_32413172$month,';', PMID_32413172$volume,'(', PMID_32413172$number,'):', PMID_32413172$pages)

PubMed_32413172 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32413172$eprint)

doi_32413172 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32413172$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
